title: what's happened to free speech?
description:
Marion Millar potentially faces prison time. For tweets. In the UK. In 2021. 
If you don't see how insane this is I don't know what to tell you.
Sign the petition: 
https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/582423 

Potential corrections:
Some news outlets report she faces up to 6 months in prison, and some report up to two years. Additionally, some are reporting she was charged under the Malicious Communications Act of 1988 and some under the Communications Act 2003. It seems more likely that it was the 2003 Communications Act due to social media, but just thought I‚Äôd bring that up to clear up any potential confusion. In the unlikely case it wasn‚Äôt the act of 2003, I believe the petition should still be signed anyway, as it‚Äôs a bad law that‚Äôs already been misused.

title: The Attack on Femininity in Fiction: Masculine Women and Disempowered Men
description:
A look at the "strong female character" in young adult literature, and why I so often have a problem with her.
